        "content": "<p>Hi all,<br>\nI've recently given this talk, \"When measurable spaces don't have enough points\". It was <em>not</em> recorded, but some people still wanted to see it, so here's an unofficial recording!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/V4WzTgjbP3c\">https://youtu.be/V4WzTgjbP3c</a></p>\n<div class=\"youtube-video message_inline_image\"><a data-id=\"V4WzTgjbP3c\" href=\"https://youtu.be/V4WzTgjbP3c\"><img src=\"https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/5913ce4359468f4e6ff42c53e794c6eb20d646d8/68747470733a2f2f692e7974696d672e636f6d2f76692f5634577a54676a625033632f64656661756c742e6a7067\"></a></div>",
